# Technical Stack - Safety Road
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.cursorrules](001-project-overview.cursorrules)

## Backend (Spring Boot)
- **Language**: Java 17 (LTS)
- **Framework**: Spring Boot 3.x
- **Build Tool**: Gradle 8.x
- **Database**: MySQL 8.x (InnoDB, utf8mb4)
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA (Hibernate 6.x)
- **Security**: Spring Security 6.x + JWT
- **Validation**: Jakarta Validation (Bean Validation 3.0)
- **Testing**: JUnit 5, Mockito, AssertJ
- **API Documentation**: Swagger/OpenAPI 3.0

## Backend Architecture
- **패키지 구조**: Domain-Driven Design (DDD) 기반
  - `backend/src/main/java/com/jinsung/safety_road_inclass/`
    - `global/`: 공통 설정, 예외 처리, 유틸리티
    - `domain/`: 비즈니스 도메인별 패키지 (7개 도메인)
- **레이어 패턴**: Controller → Service → Repository
- **DTO 변환**: Entity는 Controller에 노출 금지, DTO 매핑 필수

## Frontend (React)
- **Language**: TypeScript 5.x
- **Framework**: React 18
- **Build Tool**: Vite 5.x
- **Styling**: TailwindCSS 3.x
- **State Management**: React Context API (또는 Zustand)
- **HTTP Client**: Axios
- **Routing**: React Router 6.x
- **Form Validation**: React Hook Form + Yup/Zod
- **Testing**: Vitest, React Testing Library

## AI & Image Analysis
- **Provider**: Google Gemini Vision API (또는 OpenAI GPT-4 Vision)
- **Communication**: REST API (Backend → External AI Service)
- **Fallback**: AI 분석 실패 시 수동 검토로 폴백

## Infrastructure & Tools
- **Containerization**: Docker, Docker Compose (개발 환경)
- **Version Control**: Git, GitHub
- **API Testing**: Postman, Thunder Client
- **Database Migration**: Flyway (Schema versioning)
- **File Storage**: Local Storage (개발), AWS S3 (운영)

## Domain-Specific Tech Stack Mapping
| Domain | Tech Focus |
|:---|:---|
| **Auth** | Spring Security, JWT, BCrypt |
| **Template** | JPA Seeding (CommandLineRunner) |
| **Checklist** | Multipart File Upload, Transaction Management |
| **Review** | State Machine Pattern, Event Publishing |
| **Risk** | Business Logic Layer (위험도 계산 공식) |
| **AI** | WebClient (비동기 HTTP), External API Integration |
| **Notification** | SSE (Server-Sent Events) 또는 WebSocket |

## Development Environment
- **Java**: OpenJDK 17
- **Node.js**: v18+ (LTS)
- **MySQL**: 8.0+ (Docker 컨테이너 권장)
- **IDE**: IntelliJ IDEA (Backend), VS Code (Frontend)

